      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable surface scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some minor paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. Mechanically, the car has been well-maintained with regular oil changes, though it does have higher mileage and a slightly noisy cold start. It is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for the road, provided you don't mind the cosmetic character it has earned over the years.",
